<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0131-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0131-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p><a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0129" class="document">GWs letters to Dinwiddie</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0136" class="document">to John Stanwix</a>, as well as the <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0130" class="document">Council of War, are dated 16 June</a>.</p>

